Mauritius rupee weaker on dollar , firms on pound . The Mauritian rupee weakened against the dollar on Monday , but firmed on the pound , foreign exchange dealers at commercial banks said . The rupee was trading at a mean commercial rate of 20 . 4135 against the dollar from Friday ' s 20 . 3360 . The rupee firmed to a mean of 31 . 8615 on the pound from 31 . 8715 last Friday . 
